{
  "id": "019d286a-f2d8-78b2-92cd-578e6736ea9d",
  "content": "### Demo Config\n### Devcontainer\n\n### Pre-Ingested vs. Fresh\n\n- **Default**: Ships with pre-ingested `.corvia/knowledge/` + `hnsw_index/`. Instant demo.\n- **`--fresh`**: `corvia workspace ingest --fresh` rebuilds from scratch. User choice.\n- **Release process**: CI regenerates pre-ingested knowledge per release. Checkout repos at release tag → ingest → commit updated knowledge → tag.\n\n\n### Two Operating Modes\n\n```\nMode 1 (native):       corvia workspace init → local Ollama → develop normally\nMode 2 (devcontainer):  open in Codespaces → Ollama in container → same workspace, portable\n```\n\nThe workspace works identically in both. Devcontainer is optional packaging, not required.\n",
  "source_version": "docs/rfcs/2026-03-01-m2.1-workspace-devcontainer-design.md",
